S.FORM: "馬克白" . ( Make-pay ) nu ( inggu a kamu : Macbeth ) u masaapuyuan kalabades niSase-piya iti nugikian, u sakanamuhan nu mimelaway a piigiannu kasacacayan. sanisani sa kaladihingan ku pigiki ilabu malabades aca, u sakatawidan ku nikasaditan i piigikian, lalekalan nina giki a kitidaan sa i Su-kelan, sipakay nu gikiay a nipadadan, miawas tu balucu'ay matatebing atu sakay nu cen-ceay madademec, mitapal tu pilungucan tu sikaidaw nu tatungusan miales tu masametekay kacikiyan sadikuday a sakatademaw. .

"馬克白" . ( Make-pay ) no ( inggo a kamo : Macbeth ) o masaapoyoan kalabades niSase-piya iti nogikian, o sakanamohan no mimelaway a piigianno kasacacayan. sanisani sa kaladihingan ko pigiki ilabo malabades aca, o sakatawidan ko nikasaditan i piigikian, lalekalan nina giki a kitidaan sa i So-kelan, sipakay no gikiay a nipadadan, miawas to baloco'ay matatebing ato sakay no cen-ceay madademec, mitapal to pilongocan to sikaidaw no tatongosan miales to masametekay kacikiyan sadikoday a sakatademaw. .
